<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="159" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,438,861]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,546,572]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The distinctive characters of the new species are discussed under the diagnosis of the new monotypic genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="László" authorityYear="2022" box="[224,345,583,609]" class="Insecta" family="Nolidae" genus="Ivindonola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="159" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[224,345,583,609]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Ivindonola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="159" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,438,861]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,618,644]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Description.</emphasis>
The external and genital morphology of 
<taxonomicName authority="László, 2022" authorityName="László" authorityYear="2022" box="[787,985,619,645]" class="Insecta" family="Nolidae" genus="Ivindonola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="159" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ipassa" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[787,985,619,645]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Ivindonola ipassa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[989,1050,619,645]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[989,1050,619,645]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
are described under the description of the new monotypic genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="László" authorityYear="2022" box="[475,596,655,681]" class="Insecta" family="Nolidae" genus="Ivindonola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="159" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[475,596,655,681]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Ivindonola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,438,861]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,451,690,716]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Genetic information.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="László" authorityYear="2022" box="[461,664,691,717]" class="Insecta" family="Nolidae" genus="Ivindonola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="159" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ipassa">
<emphasis box="[461,664,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Ivindonola ipassa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been assigned the BIN URI: BOLD:AEK9606. As the species is known only from its 
<typeStatus box="[419,520,727,753]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">holotype</typeStatus>
, intraspecific genetic divergence could not be calculated. The pairwise distances between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="László" authorityYear="2022" box="[251,347,763,788]" class="Insecta" family="Nolidae" genus="Ivindonola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="159" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ipassa">
<emphasis box="[251,347,763,788]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">I. ipassa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and all other taxa discussed in this paper exceed 9%.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="159" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,438,861]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,799,825]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific name refers to the 
<typeStatus box="[707,755,799,825]" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">type</typeStatus>
locality of the new species, the Ipassa-Makokou Biosphere Reserve in central 
<collectingCountry box="[360,438,835,861]" name="Gabon" pageId="12" pageNumber="159">Gabon</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
